</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>仔仔買 M 記叫外賣員勿​​按門鈴，門口卻撞見買家爸爸無辜收負評</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/29/delivery-man-was-asked-not-to-press-the-bell-but-bumped-into-the-buyers-father-after-receiving-the-first-one-star-negative-review/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=delivery-man-was-asked-not-to-press-the-bell-but-bumped-into-the-buyers-father-after-receiving-the-first-one-star-negative-review</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 29 Dec 2021 12:02:50 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[外賣員]]></category><category><![CDATA[外賣平台]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1078714</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>外賣平台現時逐漸普及，為繁忙的都市人提供了不少便利的膳食選擇，平台的備註功能更可讓用戶仔細標明要求。近日就有一 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">外賣平台現時逐漸普及，為繁忙的都市人提供了不少便利的膳食選擇，平台的備註功能更可讓用戶仔細標明要求。近日就有一名外賣員在 Facebook 發表帖文表示，自己因為一個備註要求收到 1 顆星評價，這更是他人生的第一個負評！</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269878671_4842951485772187_3914830852834455432_n.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078721" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269878671_4842951485772187_3914830852834455432_n-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269878671_4842951485772187_3914830852834455432_n-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269878671_4842951485772187_3914830852834455432_n-1280x720.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269878671_4842951485772187_3914830852834455432_n-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269878671_4842951485772187_3914830852834455432_n-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269878671_4842951485772187_3914830852834455432_n.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Unknown.jpeg"><br /></a></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Facebook 公開群組「外送員的奇聞怪事」中有外賣員網友發文表示，有買家在訂單中備註要求外賣員千萬不要按電鈴（門鐘），因為不想</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">讓家人知道他叫麥當勞外賣，外賣員亦有乖乖照做。但在餐點送達後，買家的爸爸就剛好買完菜回家，完全是「撞到正一正」。買家爸爸在看見兒子叫了麥當勞外賣後，也順勢接下了餐點，一踏入家中便立即罵他「這麼胖了還吃麥當勞！」。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1078720 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 3.02.07-676x580.png" alt="" width="676" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 3.02.07-676x580.png 676w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 3.02.07-768x659.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 3.02.07.png 1004w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 676px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1078719 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269758696_10223318457727482_1902110443760083129_n-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269758696_10223318457727482_1902110443760083129_n-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269758696_10223318457727482_1902110443760083129_n-416x900.jpeg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269758696_10223318457727482_1902110443760083129_n-768x1663.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269758696_10223318457727482_1902110443760083129_n-710x1536.jpeg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269758696_10223318457727482_1902110443760083129_n.jpeg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">原先以為事件已告一段落，但發文者卻在事後發現，該名賣家竟然給他一顆星評價，他無奈表示：「我就得到人生第一個負評了！」。雖然他有好好照著要求沒有按下門鐘，但這種機緣巧合的意外真的讓人哭笑不得！帖子亦收到廣大網友留言回覆，表示「他只備註不要按電鈴耶&#8230;並沒有備註要躲他爸呀」、「客人一定認為你是故意拿給他爸的，真覺得你好無辜」、「覺得很可憐，但還是不小心笑出來」。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/236054837613569/?multi_permalinks=617887892763593&amp;hoisted_section_header_type=recently_seen">Facebook</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
