</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>日本 Apple 虎年限定 AirTag   送頭 2 萬名 iPhone 買家</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/29/apple-to-offer-limited-edition-airtag-as-part-of-japanese-new-year-promotion/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=apple-to-offer-limited-edition-airtag-as-part-of-japanese-new-year-promotion</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 29 Dec 2021 11:57:46 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><category><![CDATA[新年優惠]]></category><category><![CDATA[虎年]]></category><category><![CDATA[農曆新年]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1078763</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>農曆年將至，日本 Apple 亦趁此推出特別版產品以迎接虎年的到來。日本 Apple 早前宣佈，1 月 2 日 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">農曆年將至，日本 Apple 亦趁此推出特別版產品以迎接虎年的到來。日本 Apple 早前宣佈，1 月 2 日至 3 日間，向 iPhone 12、iPhone 12 mini 和 iPhone SE 的前 20,000 名購機者贈送限量的虎年限定 AirTag。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1078764" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.21.59-694x324.png" alt="" width="694" height="324" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.21.59-694x324.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.21.59-1280x598.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.21.59-768x359.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.21.59-1536x718.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.21.59-2048x957.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.21.59.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1078775" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.23.30-694x316.png" alt="" width="694" height="316" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.23.30-694x316.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.23.30-1280x583.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.23.30-768x350.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.23.30-1536x700.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.23.30-2048x934.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.23.30.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">優惠活動僅在日本境內提供，買家也必須通過官網或門店購買才可獲得禮物，在 Apple Store app 購買則沒有這項活動；官網更顯示，購買指定款的 Apple 商品更可獲得贈送的禮品卡優惠。若是購買 AirPods、AirPods Pro、AirPods Max，則可獲得面額 9000 日圓（約港幣 610 元）的 Apple 禮品卡；購買 Apple Watch Series 3、Apple Watch SE 或指定款 Apple TV，則獲得面額 6000 日圓（約港幣 406 元）的禮品卡。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1078765" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.13.10-694x289.png" alt="" width="694" height="289" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.13.10-694x289.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.13.10-1280x533.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.13.10-768x320.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.13.10-1536x639.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.13.10-2048x853.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.13.10.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1078766" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.13.59-694x312.png" alt="" width="694" h